<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Profile &amp; Settings</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&amp;family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,400&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#135bec",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#101622",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Inter", "sans-serif"],
                        "serif": ["Merriweather", "serif"],
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style>::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: transparent;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #9ca3af;
        }
        .dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #374151;
        }
        .dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #4b5563;
        }::selection {
            background: rgba(19, 91, 236, 0.2);
            color: inherit;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display overflow-hidden">
<div class="flex h-screen w-full">
<aside class="w-64 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 z-20">
<div class="flex flex-col h-full p-4 justify-between">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-2">
<div class="size-8 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-white">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">school</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<h1 class="text-base font-bold leading-none tracking-tight">VocabBuilder</h1>
<p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium mt-1">Workspace</p>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] font-variation-settings-'FILL'1">menu_book</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Library</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">database</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Vocab Bank</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">bar_chart</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Stats</span>
</a>
</nav>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2 px-3">
<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Collections</p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm" href="#">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
                        Spanish B2
                    </a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm" href="#">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                        Tech Jargon
                    </a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm" href="#">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-400"></span>
                        Daily Reads
                    </a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 pt-4">
<button class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-primary dark:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">settings</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Settings</span>
</button>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2">
<div class="size-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 overflow-hidden" data-alt="User profile picture placeholder, generic avatar" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCIQ0zQOyBitCJLtpOHL28Pb-JdGnbPhbq3BydavtVt_bu6QxlzAsBPKXEInixuVpWl0E39S0OcUDCnOK3k3xyWjGJaCTR5xBoTyzpEbeh0zOduZTY-Ak08egIDgkiRAa4oZXeQZITMPVHo6z1gsU3si0ugvBU8ZPMKCd9v5WU50UIi2m6eAARrYAuLAdCFY6F5fmzTF_I3zLN5bJzy8tw_fGfnL3PuPd0xmkaT26kRPr619ku-gy0uZYDEv7K_yofiyIREL6oM1uA'); background-size: cover;">
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-sm font-medium leading-none">Jane Doe</span>
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Free Plan</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</aside>
<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0 h-full overflow-hidden relative transition-all duration-300">
<header class="h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-8 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 z-10">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
<span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-medium">Profile &amp; Settings</span>
</div>
</header>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark scroll-smooth">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-8 px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 pb-32">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
<section>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">My Profile</h2>
<button class="text-sm text-primary font-medium hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">Save changes</button>
</div>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-sm dark:shadow-none p-6 md:p-8">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
<div class="size-24 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 overflow-hidden relative group cursor-pointer" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCIQ0zQOyBitCJLtpOHL28Pb-JdGnbPhbq3BydavtVt_bu6QxlzAsBPKXEInixuVpWl0E39S0OcUDCnOK3k3xyWjGJaCTR5xBoTyzpEbeh0zOduZTY-Ak08egIDgkiRAa4oZXeQZITMPVHo6z1gsU3si0ugvBU8ZPMKCd9v5WU50UIi2m6eAARrYAuLAdCFY6F5fmzTF_I3zLN5bJzy8tw_fGfnL3PuPd0xmkaT26kRPr619ku-gy0uZYDEv7K_yofiyIREL6oM1uA'); background-size: cover;">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white">edit</span>
</div>
</div>
<button class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 dark:hover:text-slate-300">Change Avatar</button>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Full Name</label>
<input class="w-full rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 text-sm focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary px-3 py-2" type="text" value="Jane Doe"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Email Address</label>
<input class="w-full rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 text-sm focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary px-3 py-2" type="email" value="jane.doe@example.com"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:col-span-2">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Bio</label>
<textarea class="w-full rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 text-sm focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary px-3 py-2 min-h-[80px]">Language enthusiast currently focusing on Spanish and French literature.</textarea>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section>
<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-6">Account Settings</h2>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-sm dark:shadow-none divide-y divide-slate-100 dark:divide-slate-800">
<div class="p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Password</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Last changed 3 months ago</p>
</div>
<button class="px-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
                                        Update Password
                                    </button>
</div>
<div class="p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Subscription Plan</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">You are currently on the <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Free Plan</span></p>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 px-2 py-1 rounded">Active</span>
<button class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-slate-100 text-white dark:text-slate-900 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
                                            Upgrade to Pro
                                        </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-600">Danger Zone</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Permanently delete your account and all of your content.</p>
</div>
<button class="px-4 py-2 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-900/30 text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50 dark:hover:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                                        Delete Account
                                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section>
<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-6">Preferences</h2>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-sm dark:shadow-none p-6 md:p-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Appearance</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Customize how the app looks on your device.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<label class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Theme</label>
<div class="flex gap-2">
<button class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-primary bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">light_mode</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Light</span>
</button>
<button class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500">dark_mode</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Dark</span>
</button>
<button class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500">devices</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">System</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<label class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Language</label>
<select class="w-full rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 text-sm focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary px-3 py-2">
<option>English (US)</option>
<option>Spanish</option>
<option>French</option>
<option>German</option>
</select>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="h-px bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 w-full"></div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Notifications</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Manage what emails you receive.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
<div class="flex items-center h-5">
<input class="w-4 h-4 text-primary border-slate-300 rounded focus:ring-primary" id="email-digest" type="checkbox"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="email-digest">Weekly Digest</label>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">A summary of your new vocabulary and reading stats.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
<div class="flex items-center h-5">
<input checked="" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary border-slate-300 rounded focus:ring-primary" id="email-product" type="checkbox"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="email-product">Product Updates</label>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">News about features and improvements.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
<div class="flex items-center h-5">
<input class="w-4 h-4 text-primary border-slate-300 rounded focus:ring-primary" id="email-community" type="checkbox"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="email-community">Community Challenges</label>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Notifications about new community decks and challenges.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="h-px bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 w-full"></div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Data &amp; Privacy</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Control how your data is used.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Activity History</span>
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Save your reading history to improve recommendations</span>
</div>
<label class="relative inline-flex items-center cursor-pointer">
<input checked="" class="sr-only peer" type="checkbox" value=""/>
<div class="w-11 h-6 bg-slate-200 peer-focus:outline-none peer-focus:ring-4 peer-focus:ring-blue-300 dark:peer-focus:ring-blue-800 rounded-full peer dark:bg-slate-700 peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-[2px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:border-gray-300 after:border after:rounded-full after:h-5 after:w-5 after:transition-all dark:border-gray-600 peer-checked:bg-primary"></div>
</label>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Public Profile</span>
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Allow other users to see your vocabulary collections</span>
</div>
<label class="relative inline-flex items-center cursor-pointer">
<input class="sr-only peer" type="checkbox" value=""/>
<div class="w-11 h-6 bg-slate-200 peer-focus:outline-none peer-focus:ring-4 peer-focus:ring-blue-300 dark:peer-focus:ring-blue-800 rounded-full peer dark:bg-slate-700 peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-[2px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:border-gray-300 after:border after:rounded-full after:h-5 after:w-5 after:transition-all dark:border-gray-600 peer-checked:bg-primary"></div>
</label>
</div>
<div class="mt-2">
<button class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4">Download my data</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>
</body></html>